*Dokaz* da su njihovi argumenti pogrešni je uvršten u predmet. (The evidence that their arguments are wrong is included in the case.)

U ovom slučaju *dokaz* je neophodan. (In this case, evidence is necessary.)

Oni su predočili *dokaz* da je njihova teorija tačna. (They presented evidence that their theory is correct.)

Ostavili su *dokaz* da su krivi. (They left evidence that they are guilty.)

On je dao *dokaz* da je njegov stav ispravan. (He gave evidence that his stance is correct.)